Package com.ryhma6.maven.steambeater.model.steamAPI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Achievement
    Object representation of the achievement data retrieved and parsed from SteamAPI JSON responses related to achievements.
    Friend
    Object model of the friend details from SteamAPI JSON response.
    FriendList
    Object model for friend list data retrieved and parsed from SteamAPI JSON response.
    GameData
    Object model of the game details from SteamAPI JSON response.
    GameStatistics
    Object model of the player's game statistics (including list of achievements) parsed from SteamAPI JSON.
    OwnedGames
    Object model of the JSON response from the SteamAPI (list of games owned by a player).
    PlayerProfile
    Profile data from the Steam API
    Stat
    Object model of a single stat details from SteamAPI JSON response.
